    <h2>Healthy Foods and Recipes</h2>
    <p>A healthy diet is key to good physical shape and health.Here are some ideas for foods and recipes that will improve your health:</p>

    <ul>
        <li><strong>Vegetables:</strong> Fresh salads, broccoli and spinach are excellent sources of vitamins and minerals.</li>
        <li><strong>Fruits:</strong> Apples, bananas, strawberries and kiwi are full of antioxidants and fiber.</li>
        <li><strong>Grains:</strong> Oatmeal, quinoa and brown rice will give you energy for the whole day.</li>
        <li><strong>Proteins:</strong>Eggs, fish, chicken and legumes are ideal for muscle growth.</li>
        <li><strong>Healthy fats:</strong> Avocado, olive oil and nuts support heart health.</li>
    </ul>

    <p><strong>Sample recipe for a healthy breakfast:</strong> Oatmeal with fruit and honey. Mix oatmeal with honey,strawberries and bananas for a quick and energetic breakfast.</p>
